    "attributes": {
        "action": "Base vehicle excise duty on a combination of mileage and emissions",
        "additional_details": "We think if the government are serious about reducing pollution this change could penalise those who pollute most and help those who only have a vehicle due to necessity.",
        "background": "Why should someone doing 1000 miles per annum pay the same VED as someone doing 100000? The greater the mileage the greater the pollutants and infrastructure wear and tear.",
